        Constructs a new User_Impl with specified username, password, user type, and edit permissions.
        参数:
        username - The username of the user.
        password - The password of the user.
        userType - The type of the user (e.g., admin, regular user).
        canEdit - The permission level of the user regarding edit capabilities.
